Cynthia Rothrock https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cynthia_Rothrock 0 Cynthia Ann Christine Rothrock (born March 8, 1957) is an American martial artist and actress specializing in martial arts films. Rothrock holds black belt rankings in seven styles of martial arts and was a high level competitor in martial arts before becoming an actress.
